io.prometheus.client

Class Collector

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.prometheus.client.Collector
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SimpleCollector, StandardExports

    public abstract class Collector
extends Object
    A collector for a set of metrics.

    Normal users should use Gauge, Counter and Summary. Subclasssing Collector is for advanced uses, such as proxying metrics from another monitoring system.
